https://github.com/apps/claude","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/received_events","type":"Bot","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2026-05-13T22:49:45Z","updated_at":"2026-05-13T22:49:45Z","body":"### Code review\n\nFound 2 issues:\n\n1. **`already_active` guard dropped from env snapshot trigger** — `auto_activate` is set unconditionally from `flox.features.auto_activate`, losing the `&& !already_active` gate that previously existed as `capture_env_diff`. This causes `VarsFromEnvironment::get_with_snapshot()` to allocate a full copy of the process environment on every activation, including re-activations of an already-active environment where the snapshot is meaningless.\n\nhttps://github.com/flox/flox/blob/c2e5ce288bea75f5ec3e984e2d1d196b97b8f9b0/cli/flox/src/commands/activate.rs#L460-L470\n\nThe snapshot consumer in `flox-activations`:\n\nhttps://github.com/flox/flox/blob/c2e5ce288bea75f5ec3e984e2d1d196b97b8f9b0/cli/flox-activations/src/cli/activate.rs#L88-L96\n\n2. **Hook injection not gated on `is_in_place`** — all four `gen_rc/*.rs` files inject prompt hooks (`PROMPT_COMMAND`, `precmd_functions`, `fish_prompt`, `precmd`/`cwdcmd`) whenever `args.auto_activate` is true, without checking `args.is_in_place`. For non-in-place activations (interactive subshells, `flox activate -- cmd`), the hook code is written into the subshell's rcfile, causing `flox hook-env` to spawn on every prompt in an already-activated shell. The existing `should_source` logic in the same file shows the expected pattern (`!args.is_in_place`), but the hook block does not follow it. `ZshStartupArgs` also lacks an `is_in_place` field entirely, so the guard cannot even be added there without a struct change.\n\nhttps://github.com/flox/flox/blob/c2e5ce288bea75f5ec3e984e2d1d196b97b8f9b0/cli/flox-activations/src/gen_rc/bash.rs#L45-L50\n\nhttps://github.com/flox/flox/blob/c2e5ce288bea75f5ec3e984e2d1d196b97b8f9b0/cli/flox-activations/src/gen_rc/bash.rs#L154-L161\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)\n\n<sub>- If this code review was useful, please react with 👍. Otherwise, react with 👎.</sub>","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/flox/flox/issues/comments/4445790023/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":0,"-1":1,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":{"id":1236702,"client_id":"Iv23liqTIFEtdIu6Vn1r","slug":"claude","node_id":"A_kwHOBIuudM4AEt7e","owner":{"login":"anthropics","id":76263028,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjc2MjYzMDI4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/76263028?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/anthropics","html_url":"https://github.com/anthropics","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/anthropics/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/anthropics/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/anthropics/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/anthropics/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/anthropics/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/anthropics/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/anthropics/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/anthropics/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://ap